title: ROB MACHADO GOES FOR A DOWN-WINDER
description:
Rob Machado and friends go for a scary, windy SUP adventure. The crew starts at Turtle Bay, rides open ocean swells down wind and eventually ends up back on dry land at Waimea Bay. 

Video: PK
